overview:
Attorney Scott C. Gottlieb, Injury Law Attorney, located in New York, will fight for you! Our firm has a successful track record of securing results for victims of car accidents, medical malpractice, wrongful death claims, and other injury / accident lawsuits.

Our goals are the same as yours: To get the maximum compensation you are entitled to from the insurance company. Our Binghamton Personal Injury Lawyers know that it is about the money. We also know what it takes to get your New York personal injury case resolved in your favor. Hard work, honesty, respect and experience are the keys to winning — and that’s what you can expect from Scott C. Gottlieb, Injury Law Attorney.
